{"title":"紫砂壶","authors":["宁宇"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫砂壶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宜兴泡在小小的紫砂壶里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山碧绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水碧绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有洞口和岩石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"裸露出紫砂的深沉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有太阳长驻的脸庞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁紫酱色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳朴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宜兴乘着小小的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫砂茶壶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走出水乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是游子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小小的圆圆的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壶嘴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒出碧碧绿的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思乡水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杯茶下肚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如卧在青山绿水间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看渔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看变幻的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那颜色那味儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那说不出的柔情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要捧起紫砂壶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无言心曲通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血水相融汇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是江南的泥捏就"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是太湖的水拌和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是燧人氏的火烧炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是陆羽的《茶经》催生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你信不信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使你我化为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青烟一缕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土一抔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也总带有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫砂壶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶的香味"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}